Package hrps.control

Class OrderController

  • java.lang.Object
    • hrps.control.OrderController
  • public class OrderController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the controller for room service orders, includes create, update, search for orders and calculate prices of orders.
    Author:
    Peng Wenxuan
